---
import FadeIn from "./FadeIn.tsx"
import imageSolution from "/src/assets/img/manUsingGlasses2-v2.avif";
---

<section id="benefits" class="py-10 mt-3 lg:mt-0 md:pt-0 lg:py-16 xl:pb-5 lg:flex lg:justify-center">
  <div class="container px-4 md:px-6 lg:flex lg:flex-col lg:items-center">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-start gap-5 mb-5 lg:mb-0 lg:text-center lg:self-center lg:w-[70%]">
    {/* Header Section */}
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-6 mb-6 lg:mb-14 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-amber-500/10 border border-amber-500/30">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="#f59e0b" class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-filled icon-tabler-clipboard-check"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M17.997 4.17a3 3 0 0 1 2.003 2.83v12a3 3 0 0 1 -3 3h-10a3 3 0 0 1 -3 -3v-12a3 3 0 0 1 2.003 -2.83a4 4 0 0 0 3.997 3.83h4a4 4 0 0 0 3.98 -3.597zm-3.704 7.123l-3.293 3.292l-1.293 -1.292a1 1 0 1 0 -1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 0 0 1.414 0l4 -4a1 1 0 0 0 -1.414 -1.414m-.293 -9.293a2 2 0 1 1 0 4h-4a2 2 0 1 1 0 -4z" /></svg>
            <span class="text-xs lg:text-sm font-semibold text-amber-400 uppercase tracking-wide">
              Tecnología Comprobada
            </span>
          </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold text-center text-brand-headline">
          3 Problemas Que Desaparecen al Usar Tus Gafas
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-center mt-1 lg:text-xl lg:tracking-wider text-brand-body">
          Miles de profesionales, estudiantes y gamers ya recuperaron su bienestar visual. Los resultados son inmediatos y medibles.
        </p>
    </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <FadeIn delay={100} client:visible>
        <div class="border shadow-lg h-full p-6 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 group relative bg-bg-card-glass border-white/20 rounded-2xl hover:border-amber-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-amber-500/20 group">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-orange-600 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg  width="24"  height="24"  viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none"  stroke="#ffffff"  stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round"  stroke-linejoin="round"  class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-eye"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M10 12a2 2 0 1 0 4 0a2 2 0 0 0 -4 0" /><path d="M21 12c-2.4 4 -5.4 6 -9 6c-3.6 0 -6.6 -2 -9 -6c2.4 -4 5.4 -6 9 -6c3.6 0 6.6 2 9 6" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-headline">Alivio Ocular Inmediato</h3>
          <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 border border-green-500/40">
                  <span class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400">
                   87% menos fatiga
                  </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-body">
            Elimina el ardor, sequedad e irritación que sientes después de 8+ horas frente a pantallas. Tus ojos se sienten descansados desde el primer día de uso.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-amber-400 font-medium">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                  <path d="M12 2c5.523 0 10 4.477 10 10s-4.477 10-10 10S2 17.523 2 12 6.477 2 12 2zm0 5a1 1 0 0 0-.993.883L11 8v4l.007.117a1 1 0 0 0 .876.876L12 13h3l.117-.007a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.986L12.883 11H13v-3l-.007-.117A1 1 0 0 0 12 7z" />
                </svg>
                <span>Resultados en 24 horas</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </FadeIn>      
      <FadeIn delay={100} client:visible>
        <div class="border shadow-lg h-full p-6 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 group relative bg-bg-card-glass border-white/20 rounded-2xl hover:border-amber-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-amber-500/20">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-orange-600 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg  width="24"  height="24"  viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none"  stroke="#ffffff"  stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round"  stroke-linejoin="round"  class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-moon"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 3c.132 0 .263 0 .393 0a7.5 7.5 0 0 0 7.92 12.446a9 9 0 1 1 -8.313 -12.454z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-headline">Sueño Más Profundo</h3>
          <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 border border-green-500/40">
                  <span class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400">
                   43 min más de sueño
                  </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-body">
            La luz azul interfiere con la producción de melatonina, afectando tu descanso. Usa nuestras gafas antes de dormir y despierta renovado.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-amber-400 font-medium">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                  <path d="M12 2c5.523 0 10 4.477 10 10s-4.477 10-10 10S2 17.523 2 12 6.477 2 12 2zm0 5a1 1 0 0 0-.993.883L11 8v4l.007.117a1 1 0 0 0 .876.876L12 13h3l.117-.007a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.986L12.883 11H13v-3l-.007-.117A1 1 0 0 0 12 7z" />
                </svg>
                <span>Mejora desde la 1era noche</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </FadeIn>
      <FadeIn delay={100} client:visible>
        <div class="border shadow-lg h-full p-6 flex flex-col items-center gap-3 group relative bg-bg-card-glass border-white/20 rounded-2xl hover:border-amber-500/50 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02] hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-amber-500/20 group">
          <div class="h-12 w-12 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-500 to-orange-600 flex items-center justify-center">
            <svg  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"  width="24"  height="24"  viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="none"  stroke="#ffffff"  stroke-width="2"  stroke-linecap="round"  stroke-linejoin="round"  class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-alert-triangle"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M12 9v4" /><path d="M10.363 3.591l-8.106 13.534a1.914 1.914 0 0 0 1.636 2.871h16.214a1.914 1.914 0 0 0 1.636 -2.87l-8.106 -13.536a1.914 1.914 0 0 0 -3.274 0z" /><path d="M12 16h.01" /></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-headline">Cero Dolores de Cabeza</h3>
          <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-green-500/20 border border-green-500/40">
                  <span class="text-sm font-bold text-green-400">
                   91% reducción
                  </span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-brand-body lg:grow">
            Despídete de las migrañas por tensión visual. Trabaja, estudia o mira series sin molestias.
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-amber-400 font-medium ">
                <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                  <path d="M12 2c5.523 0 10 4.477 10 10s-4.477 10-10 10S2 17.523 2 12 6.477 2 12 2zm0 5a1 1 0 0 0-.993.883L11 8v4l.007.117a1 1 0 0 0 .876.876L12 13h3l.117-.007a1 1 0 0 0 0-1.986L12.883 11H13v-3l-.007-.117A1 1 0 0 0 12 7z" />
                </svg>
                <span>Notable en 48 horas</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </FadeIn>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-14 xl:mt-20 rounded-xl p-1 lg:p-2 shadow-lg bg-bg-card-glass group">
      <div class="grid gap-2 lg:grid-cols-2 items-center">
        <div class="relative h-[300px] md:h-[400px] lg:h-[500px] rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
          <img
            src={imageSolution.src}
            alt="Persona usando gafas con filtro de luz azul"
            class="object-cover w-full h-full"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="xl:self-baseline xl:pt-2">
          <h3 class="text-2xl text-brand-headline font-bold text-center mb-6 xl:text-3xl">
            Por Qué Nuestras Gafas Son <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-300 to-orange-400">Superiores</span>
          </h3>
          <ul class="space-y-8 text-brand-body">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg  width="60"  height="60"   viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="#05df72"  class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-filled icon-tabler-shield-check max-w-[4rem]"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M11.998 2l.118 .007l.059 .008l.061 .013l.111 .034a.993 .993 0 0 1 .217 .112l.104 .082l.255 .218a11 11 0 0 0 7.189 2.537l.342 -.01a1 1 0 0 1 1.005 .717a13 13 0 0 1 -9.208 16.25a1 1 0 0 1 -.502 0a13 13 0 0 1 -9.209 -16.25a1 1 0 0 1 1.005 -.717a11 11 0 0 0 7.531 -2.527l.263 -.225l.096 -.075a.993 .993 0 0 1 .217 -.112l.112 -.034a.97 .97 0 0 1 .119 -.021l.115 -.007zm3.71 7.293a1 1 0 0 0 -1.415 0l-3.293 3.292l-1.293 -1.292l-.094 -.083a1 1 0 0 0 -1.32 1.497l2 2l.094 .083a1 1 0 0 0 1.32 -.083l4 -4l.083 -.094a1 1 0 0 0 -.083 -1.32z" /></svg>
              <div class="xl:flex xl:flex-col xl:gap-2">
                <span class="font-semibold text-[17px] xl:text-lg">
                  Bloquean hasta el 99% de la Luz Azul Más Dañina
                </span>
                <p class=" mt-0.5">
                  A diferencia de las gafas "transparentes" que filtran apenas 20-30%, nuestras lentes ámbar bloquean las longitudes de onda más dañinas (415-455nm). Verás un ligero tinte cálido, pero es ese filtrado profundo lo que realmente protege tus ojos y tu sueño.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg  width="60"  height="60"   viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="#05df72"  class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-filled icon-tabler-shield-check"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M11.998 2l.118 .007l.059 .008l.061 .013l.111 .034a.993 .993 0 0 1 .217 .112l.104 .082l.255 .218a11 11 0 0 0 7.189 2.537l.342 -.01a1 1 0 0 1 1.005 .717a13 13 0 0 1 -9.208 16.25a1 1 0 0 1 -.502 0a13 13 0 0 1 -9.209 -16.25a1 1 0 0 1 1.005 -.717a11 11 0 0 0 7.531 -2.527l.263 -.225l.096 -.075a.993 .993 0 0 1 .217 -.112l.112 -.034a.97 .97 0 0 1 .119 -.021l.115 -.007zm3.71 7.293a1 1 0 0 0 -1.415 0l-3.293 3.292l-1.293 -1.292l-.094 -.083a1 1 0 0 0 -1.32 1.497l2 2l.094 .083a1 1 0 0 0 1.32 -.083l4 -4l.083 -.094a1 1 0 0 0 -.083 -1.32z" /></svg>
              <div class="xl:flex xl:flex-col xl:gap-2">
                <span class="font-semibold text-[17px] xl:text-lg">
                  Favorecen un Sueño Profundo y Reparador
                </span>
                <p class=" mt-0.5">
                  La luz azul artificial suprime tu melatonina natural y confunde tu cerebro sobre cuándo dormir. Úsalas 2-3 horas antes de acostarte para restaurar tu ciclo natural: conciliarás el sueño más rápido y despertarás profundamente descansado.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
              <svg width="60"  height="60"  viewBox="0 0 24 24"  fill="#05df72"  class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-filled icon-tabler-shield-check max-w-[1rem]"><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"/><path d="M11.998 2l.118 .007l.059 .008l.061 .013l.111 .034a.993 .993 0 0 1 .217 .112l.104 .082l.255 .218a11 11 0 0 0 7.189 2.537l.342 -.01a1 1 0 0 1 1.005 .717a13 13 0 0 1 -9.208 16.25a1 1 0 0 1 -.502 0a13 13 0 0 1 -9.209 -16.25a1 1 0 0 1 1.005 -.717a11 11 0 0 0 7.531 -2.527l.263 -.225l.096 -.075a.993 .993 0 0 1 .217 -.112l.112 -.034a.97 .97 0 0 1 .119 -.021l.115 -.007zm3.71 7.293a1 1 0 0 0 -1.415 0l-3.293 3.292l-1.293 -1.292l-.094 -.083a1 1 0 0 0 -1.32 1.497l2 2l.094 .083a1 1 0 0 0 1.32 -.083l4 -4l.083 -.094a1 1 0 0 0 -.083 -1.32z" /></svg>
              <div class="xl:flex xl:flex-col xl:gap-2">
                <span class="font-semibold text-[17px] xl:text-lg">
                  Reducen la Fatiga Ocular y los Dolores de Cabeza
                </span>
                <p class=" mt-0.5">
                  Úsalas durante tu jornada digital y nota el cambio en tus ojos: menos tensión visual y sin esa presión incómoda en la frente después de horas de pantalla.
                </p>
              </div>
            </li>
            
            
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
